    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 76-77.</p><p>Warlock’s Chosen</p><p>Prerequisite: Level 25+ Warlock, Warlock’s Champion Invocation</p><p>Your servant remains at your side indefinitely until destroyed or dismissed. If destroyed, you cannot summon it again until you finish a long rest. Your servant’s CR can be up to 21. You can retain a lower CR servant if you choose, and work with your DM to bring it up to a fitting CR 21 stat block.</p></div>",
